<p>How can i remove an Item <strong>(QSpacerItem)</strong> from a Layout? I am defining my QSpacerItem as follows:</p>  <pre><code>    spacerItem =  QSpacerItem(20,80,QSizePolicy.Minimum,QSizePolicy.Expanding)      n = self.grid.rowCount() + 1     self.grid.addItem(spacerItem, n, 1)     self.grid.setRowStretch(n, 100) </code></pre>  <p>I want the <strong>spacerItem</strong> to be always the last Element in my Layout, so when i add a new Widget, i want to remove the <strong>spacerItem</strong>, add the new Widget and then append the spacerItem to the End.</p>